stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE : App starts\n(no active round)

    IDLE --> TRIGGERED : Doctor uploads scan\n→ POST /round/start to FL Coordinator

    TRIGGERED --> LOCAL_TRAINING : FL Coordinator begins\nhospital simulation loop

    LOCAL_TRAINING --> LOCAL_TRAINING : Each hospital completes\nlocal training epoch\n(progress callback fires per hospital)

    LOCAL_TRAINING --> AGGREGATING : All 3 hospitals complete\nlocal training

    AGGREGATING --> COMPLETE : FedAvg / FedProx applied\nwebhook fires to NestJS\nDB updated

    COMPLETE --> IDLE : Ready for next trigger\n(fl:active key deleted from Redis)

    LOCAL_TRAINING --> FAILED : Timeout (>120s) or\nFL Coordinator error

    AGGREGATING --> FAILED : Aggregation math error or\nwebhook delivery failure

    FAILED --> IDLE : Error logged to system\n(FlRound saved with error status)

    note right of TRIGGERED
        round_id generated.
        Stored in Redis:
        fl:active:{hospitalId} = roundId
        TTL: 10 minutes
    end note

    note right of LOCAL_TRAINING
        Hospital A: done → Hospital B: done → Hospital C: done
        WS event fl:round:progress fired per hospital.
        Topology node pulses green as each finishes.
    end note

    note right of AGGREGATING
        Weight deltas averaged — no raw data involved.
        Δw_global = Σ(n_k/n × Δw_k)
        ~3 seconds in mock mode.
    end note

    note right of COMPLETE
        FlRound row saved.
        FlContribution ×3 rows saved.
        PrivacyAuditLog ×3 rows written.
        rawDataTransmitted=0 (FL privacy invariant).
        WS event fl:round:complete broadcast.
    end note
